	</section>

	<section class="speakers">
		<div class="inner">

			<h2>Speakers</h2>
			<h3>Sit back and get inspired.</h3>

			<ul>

			<% speakers.forEach(function(speaker) { %>

				<li class="media">	

					<div class="img">
						<% if (speaker.url.length) { %>
							<a class="web" href="<%= speaker.url %>" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-link"></i></a>
						<% } else { %>
							<span class="spacer"></span>
						<% } %>

						<img src="<%= speaker.avatar %>">

						<% if (speaker.twitter.length) { %>
							<a class="twitter" href="<%= speaker.twitter %>" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
						<% } else { %>
							<span class="spacer"></span>
						<% } %>
					</div>
					<div class="media-body">
						<h3><%- speaker.name %></h3>
						<p><%- speaker.title %></p>
						<p><%- speaker.intro %></p>
					</div>
				</li>
			<% }) %>


			</ul>

		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="tickets">
		<div class="inner">
			<h2>Tickets</h2>
			<p>We are building upon the <a href="http://copenhagenjs.dk" target="_blank">CopenhagenJS</a> and <a href="http://thewcdc.net" target="_blank">TheWCDC.</a> communities to create a unique day, where we focus on what it takes to build for the web.</p>
			<p>A ticket for ColdFront will include lunch, tea/coffee/water and plenty of beer in the night. An early-bid ticket will set you back 1500 DKK + VAT. Regular bird will be 2000 DKK + VAT, and for the late birds the price will be 2500,- DKK.</p>
			<p>To get you in the ColdFront-mood we are also organizing jam-sessions in a bar on the night before the conference. </p>
			<p>This means two nights full of talks and fun - all included with your ticket! </p>
			<iframe allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" hspace="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" scrolling="true" src="http://billetto.dk/en/events/44757/widget/" vspace="0" width="100%" height="287"></iframe>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="location">
